title: #79a: We Are Anonymous (Luke Harder, Star_Fawkes)
itunes:title: We Are Anonymous - Part 1
description: Luke Harder and Star_Fawkes met me at the Comedy Store to talk about Anonymous. It was a really enlightening conversation. I think we all got the wrong idea about these guys. This is one to spread around.
